result.longName: Jilin Liyuan Precision Manufacturing Co., Ltd.

assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Jilin Liyuan Precision Manufacturing Co., Ltd. manufactures and sells aluminum alloy machinery products in China. The company offers bumpers, battery boxes, door and window profiles, curtain walls, all-aluminum home, rail car nose, body profile, solar frame, solar bracket, laptop shell, smartphone body, oil drill pipe, reducer tube and all kinds of seamless tube, etc. It provides aluminum deep processing parts; car bodies and containers; bars and pipes; and tempered, insulating, laminated, bulletproof, and fireproof glass, as well as water conservancy projects, I-shaped aluminum, and flyovers and three-dimensional parking garages. The company products are used in auto parts, building decoration, rail transit, solar energy, electronic power, aviation, and petrochemical industries. It also exports its products. The company was formerly known as Jilin Liyuan Aluminum Co., Ltd. and changed its name to Jilin Liyuan Precision Manufacturing Co., Ltd. in November 2013. Jilin Liyuan Precision Manufacturing Co., Ltd. was founded in 2000 and is based in Liaoyuan, China.
